# Meme Prompts

## Format

These should be simple, fast, and easy to produce.

## Starter prompts

1. GTA 6 character reacts to London rent prices.
2. GTA 6 character tries to make money online with zero skills.
3. GTA 6 NPC starts a side hustle and becomes more successful than the main character.
4. GTA 6 criminal discovers AI tools and becomes a content creator.
5. GTA 6 style character follows bad online business advice and instantly regrets it.

## Style notes

- Funny
- Fast pacing
- Relatable
- Built around trending audio when possible
- 15 to 30 seconds
